-- 
De Jager Calls for Europe, U.S. Economic Reform, ANP Reports

-- B y   F r e d   P a l s
-- 
2011-08-06T14:08:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-06/de-jager-calls-for-europe-u-s-economic-reform-anp-reports.html
Economic reforms and budgetary
discipline are necessary for all of  Europe  and essential to the
U.S., local news agency ANP cited Dutch Finance Minister  Jan
Kees de Jager  as saying, without reporting how it obtained the
information.  The Netherlands has faith in the  U.S. economy  and a fast
and thorough implementation of budgetary reforms is essential,
ANP cited De Jager as saying, commenting on the downgrade of the
U.S. debt rating.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Pals in Amsterdam at 
 fpals@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net  